entry.summary:
Vendor: Chateau
Type: Disposables
Price: 5.99

Chateau - Compact Luggage Scale 75 Lbs Capacity, LS-75

The Stop-N-Lock Luggage Scale from Chateau allows for a simple affordable solution to eliminate pre-trip packing guesswork and hefty overweight luggage fees.

This easy to use luggage scale has a patented stop and lock feature. Two hands track the weight of the bag and the second hand stops and locks at that weight so you can set the suitcase down to read the dial.

It also includes a tape measure to also ensure bags are not oversized. Take it with you on your trip to ensure you don't tip the scales on your way back. 

  • Weighs up to 32 kg (75 lbs)
  • Metric & Imperial display
  • 1 meter (39 inches) tape measure integrated
  • Ideal for the traveler
  • Save costs for overweight luggage
